application

Class Settings

  • java.lang.Object
    • application.Settings

  • public class Settings
extends java.lang.Object
    Class containing static queries for retrieving resultsets from DBPedia and WikiData as well as the ASK queries for validation. Also contains the endpoints for the two knowledge graphs.
